decks.notes: The deck focuses on utilizing aggressive creatures and versatile spells to control the board and disrupt the opponent's strategy. With Aragorn, King of Gondor as the commander, the deck includes a variety of powerful creatures and spells to apply pressure and maintain control of the battlefield. Cards like Mother of Runes, Brazen Borrower, and Skyclave Apparition provide protection and removal options, while counterspells like Force of Will and Mana Leak help disrupt the opponent's game plan. The deck also includes efficient removal spells like Lightning Bolt and Swords to Plowshares to deal with threats. Overall, the strategy revolves around deploying threats quickly, disrupting the opponent, and maintaining a strong board presence to secure victory.
